        RHG Compute Tools
        =================
        
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/rhg_compute_tools.svg
                :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/rhg_compute_tools
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/RhodiumGroup/rhg_compute_tools.svg
